="showSection('summary')"><span class="checkmark">‚úì</span>REFLECTION</div></div></div><div class="content-container"><div class="content-header"><div class="mobile-menu-btn" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()">‚ò∞</div><div class="content-title"><h1>PRE-WORK MICROLEARNING - INTRODUCTION</h1><div class="lesson-info">Lesson 1 of 1</div><h2>INTRODUCTION TO DEI</h2></div><div class="logo-placeholder"><img src="https://i.postimg.cc/9FkZdTvQ/taa-circles-only-no-TAA-png.png" alt="TAA Logo"></div></div><div class="main-content">
                    <div class="section active" id="learning_intent">
                        <div class="section-header"><h3>LEARNING INTENT</h3></div>
                        <div class="section-content"><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div style="position: relative; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><div class="key-definition-box"><h4>WELCOME TO YOUR DEI JOURNEY</h4><div><p>This microlearning module is designed to give you a clear, practical understanding of <strong>Diversity, Equity, and Inclusion (DEI)</strong> ‚Äî three interconnected concepts that shape how we work together, lead others, and build thriving teams.</p>

<p>Whether you're new to these ideas or looking for a refresher, this 10‚Äì15 minute session will provide you with foundational knowledge you can apply immediately in your day-to-day work.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 15px;"><strong>Duration:</strong> 10‚Äì15 minutes</p></div></div></div></div></div>
