                    <div class="section" id="objectives">
                        <div class="section-header"><h3>OBJECTIVES</h3></div>
                        <div class="section-content"><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="text-content-render"><p><strong>By the end of this module, you will be able to:</strong></p>

<ul>
<li>Define <strong>Diversity</strong>, <strong>Equity</strong>, and <strong>Inclusion</strong> in plain English</li>
<li>Recognise the difference between <strong>Equity</strong> and <strong>Equality</strong></li>
<li>Understand why <strong>Inclusion</strong> matters for performance, innovation, and wellbeing</li>
<li>Reflect on how DEI shows up in your own workplace</li>
</ul></div></div></div>
