                    </div>

                    <div class="section" id="practice">
                        <div class="section-header"><h3>WHY INCLUSION MATTERS</h3></div>
                        <div class="section-content"><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="text-content-render"><p>Inclusion isn't just the right thing to do ‚Äî it delivers real, measurable benefits for individuals, teams, and organisations. Here's why it matters:</p></div></div>

<div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="benefits-grid">
<div class="benefit-card">
<div class="icon">üìà</div>
<h5>Performance</h5>
<p>When people feel included, they're more engaged, motivated, and committed. They bring their full selves to work ‚Äî and their best ideas.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #667eea;"><strong>Research shows:</strong> Inclusive teams outperform their peers by up to 80% in team-based assessments.</p>
</div>
<div class="benefit-card">
<div class="icon">üí°</div>
<h5>Innovation</h5>
<p>Diverse perspectives lead to better problem-solving and more creative solutions. But only if those perspectives are heard ‚Äî that's where inclusion comes in.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #667eea;"><strong>Research shows:</strong> Companies with above-average diversity produce 19% more revenue from innovation.</p>
</div>
<div class="benefit-card">
<div class="icon">‚ù§Ô∏è</div>
<h5>Wellbeing</h5>
<p>Feeling excluded takes a toll on mental health. Inclusion creates psychological safety ‚Äî a sense that it's okay to speak up, take risks, and be yourself.</p>
<p style="margin-top: 10px; font-size: 13px; color: #667eea;"><strong>Research shows:</strong> Employees who feel included are 3x more likely to feel excited about and committed to their work.</p>
</div>
</div></div>

<div class="section-content-wrapper"><div style="position: relative; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><div class="key-definition-box"><h4>THE INCLUSION EQUATION</h4><div><p style="font-size: 18px; text-align: center; padding: 20px 0;"><strong>Diversity + Equity + Inclusion = Belonging</strong></p>

<p>Each element plays a vital role:</p>
<ul>
<li><strong>Diversity</strong> brings different people to the table.</li>
<li><strong>Equity</strong> ensures everyone has a fair chance to contribute.</li>
<li><strong>Inclusion</strong> makes sure every voice is heard and valued.</li>
</ul>

<p style="margin-top: 15px;">Together, they create a culture where people don't just show up ‚Äî they <em>belong</em>. And when people belong, they thrive.</p></div></div></div></div></div>
                        <div class="navigation-buttons">
                            <button class="nav-btn" onclick="previousSection()">Previous</button>
                            <button class="nav-btn next" onclick="nextSection()">Continue</button>
                        </div>
