                    <div class="section" id="summary">
                        <div class="section-header"><h3>REFLECTION</h3></div>
                        <div class="section-content"><div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="reflection-box">
<div class="time-badge">‚è±Ô∏è 1-Minute Reflection</div>
<h4>Think About Your Workplace</h4>
<p>Take a moment to consider the three components of DEI ‚Äî <strong>Diversity</strong>, <strong>Equity</strong>, and <strong>Inclusion</strong> ‚Äî in your own work environment.</p>
</div></div>

<div class="section-content-wrapper"><div class="feedback-box-render"><h4>Reflection Question:</h4>
<p style="margin: 15px 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.8;">Which of the three ‚Äî <strong>Diversity</strong>, <strong>Equity</strong>, or <strong>Inclusion</strong> ‚Äî do you see <em>most</em> in your workplace? Which do you see <em>least</em>?</p>
<p style="margin-bottom: 15px; font-size: 14px; color: #666;">Consider specific examples: team composition, how decisions are made, who gets opportunities, how meetings are run, whose voices are heard.</p>
<textarea placeholder="Type your reflection here... There are no right or wrong answers ‚Äî this is for your own learning."></textarea></div></div>

<div class="section-content-wrapper"><div style="position: relative; margin: 20px 0; padding: 0;"><div class="key-definition-box"><h4>KEY TAKEAWAYS</h4><div><ul>
<li><strong>Diversity</strong> is about who is in the room ‚Äî the range of differences present.</li>
<li><strong>Equity</strong> is about fairness ‚Äî giving people what they need to succeed.</li>
<li><strong>Inclusion</strong> is about belonging ‚Äî ensuring everyone can fully participate and be valued.</li>
<li><strong>Equality</strong> treats everyone the same; <strong>Equity</strong> recognises different needs.</li>
<li>Inclusion drives <strong>performance</strong>, <strong>innovation</strong>, and <strong>wellbeing</strong>.</li>
</ul>

